Photographer, specialized in post-production and digital retouching. Student of art and design.
He combines the work in postproduction of the image for the photographer Roger Grasas with the realization of his personal project.
His personal work is based on the visual arts. It focuses from looking and tracking the landscape.
The city and its area of residential and industrial influence grow, devastating on the one hand, but on the other leaving spaces free of its original use, in a state of transition, disused.